&nbsp;
All over Turkey, turnout was well over 90%, in fact, 61.4 million. At the moment the total waste is 43%. However the Chp and the opposition are confirmed on the Mediterranean and Aegean coast, while the center of Anatolia and the Black Sea remain at the party of Erdogan.
